Package io.github.shuoros.jfiler.file

Class Folder

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.io.File
      • io.github.shuoros.jfiler.file.File
        • io.github.shuoros.jfiler.file.Folder
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<File>
    public class Folder
extends File
    A model that inherits File and represents a folder (which is itself a type of file). This class, in addition to the information in the file class, holds the folder size and a list of all the files it contains.
    Since:
    1.0.0
    Version:
    1.0.0
    Author:
    Soroush Shemshadi
    See Also:
    File, Serialized Form
